  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "SEC1",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Transportation Lane Master Data"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "A Transportation Lane defines the valid path between two locations in SAP TM. It specifies how goods can move from a source location to a destination location using one or more transportation modes. Transportation planning and optimization rely heavily on correctly maintained transportation lanes."
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC3",
      "type": "callout",
      "calloutType": "important",
      "title": "Key Concept",
      "content": "Transportation Lanes answer the question: 'Can goods be transported from Location A to Location B, and if yes, how?'"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC4",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Purpose of Transportation Lanes"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC5",
      "type": "bullet-list",
      "items": [
        "Define valid transportation routes",
        "Support route determination",
        "Enable transportation planning",
        "Determine transportation modes",
        "Support carrier selection",
        "Improve optimization accuracy"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC6",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Transportation Lane Components"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC7",
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Transportation Lane Attributes",
      "headers": [
        "Attribute",
        "Description"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Source Location",
          "Shipment origin"
        ],
        [
          "Destination Location",
          "Shipment destination"
        ],
        [
          "Means of Transport",
          "Road, Rail, Air or Ocean"
        ],
        [
          "Carrier",
          "Transportation provider"
        ],
        [
          "Distance",
          "Used for planning and costing"
        ],
        [
          "Transit Time",
          "Expected travel duration"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC8",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Transportation Lane Planning"
    },
    {
